	" is a maze game developed and published by Atari for its Atari 2600 system in 1980. Described in the manual as a "maze of city blocks", the player, either a red or blue cop on patrol needs to escape a randomly generated maze as quickly as possible. On some variants present in the game, the player additionally has to either avoid or capture robber blocks, depending on the setting.
